{"word":"ἀλλάσσω","slug":"ἀλλάσσω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἀλλάσσω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἄλλος\">ἄλλος</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘to cause <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a> to be different’, <b><i>change</i> <a href='B:510 6:14'>Ac 6:14</a>; <a href='B:550 4:20'>Gal 4:20</a>; <i>transform</i> <a href='B:530 15:51'>1 Cor 15:51f</a>; <a href='B:650 1:12'>Hb 1:12</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘to substitute one thing for another’<b>, <i>exchange</i></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ acc.\">acc.</a> followed by <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐν\">ἐν</a></el> (<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <a href='B:230 105:20'>Psalm 105:20</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ LXX\">LXX</a>; the syntax is not unknown in standard Greek) instead of simple <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ gen.\">gen.</a> <b><a href='B:520 1:23'>Ro 1:23</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀλλά\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀλλαχόθεν\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}